sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant QP as Queue Proxy<br/>(sidecar)
    participant Server as autogluonserver<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant AG as AutoGluon Predictor<br/>(in-process)
    participant FS as /mnt/models<br/>(filesystem)
    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>(init container)
    participant Remote as Remote Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over StorageInit,Remote: Flow 1: Model Loading (pod startup)

    StorageInit->>Remote: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials (Secret)
    Remote-->>StorageInit: Model files
    StorageInit->>FS: Write to /mnt/models

    Note over Server,AG: Model Auto-Detection

    Server->>FS: Read model directory
    FS-->>Server: Model files
    Server->>AG: Try TimeSeriesPredictor.load()
    alt TimeSeriesPredictor found
        AG-->>Server: TimeSeriesPredictor loaded
    else Fallback to TabularPredictor
        Server->>AG: TabularPredictor.load()
        AG-->>Server: TabularPredictor loaded
    end

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 2: Tabular Inference (v1 REST)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
    Gateway->>QP: Forward request
    QP->>Server: HTTP/8080<br/>(pod-internal, no TLS)
    Server->>AG: TabularPredictor.predict()<br/>(in-process)
    AG-->>Server: Prediction result
    Server-->>QP: JSON response
    QP-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction result

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 3: Time Series Inference (v1 REST)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
    Gateway->>QP: Forward request
    QP->>Server: HTTP/8080<br/>JSON: {instances, known_covariates}
    Server->>AG: TimeSeriesPredictor.predict()<br/>use_cache=False<br/>(in-process)
    AG-->>Server: Forecast result
    Server-->>QP: JSON response
    QP-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON forecast result

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 4: Tabular Inference (v2 REST)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
    Gateway->>QP: Forward request
    QP->>Server: HTTP/8080<br/>v2 InferRequest (tensors)
    Server->>Server: _infer_request_to_dataframe()<br/>Map tensors → DataFrame
    Server->>AG: TabularPredictor.predict()<br/>(in-process)
    AG-->>Server: Prediction result
    Server->>Server: _build_v2_outputs()<br/>regression/classification/proba/quantile
    Server-->>QP: v2 InferResponse
    QP-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: v2 tensor response
